37395>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37395>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37396>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37397>>>    End_Procedure
37398>>>    
37398>>>End_Object
